ğŸ“ Educational Value

This project demonstrates key embedded systems concepts:

Peripheral integration

Serial communication (UART)

Real-time control logic

Modular software design

State machines and mode arbitration

It goes beyond single-sensor examples by showing how multiple input sources can coexist in a reliable embedded system.
